Generic single-database configuration.

# init db with alembic
## Step 1: init alembic folder
- alembic init alembic
## step 2: config your env file
- in current env file we import our meta data, add sys path as alembic folder is not in our app
- config your sqlalchemy.url in your alembic.ini file, as it is secret do not push it to your source code management
## step 3: generate init db script file
- alembic revision --autogenerate -m "auto-generate migration"
